+## Consistency
+The runbook follows the established style of `docs/r750-bare-metal-runbook.md`, using H1 titles, part-style H2 sections, tables for configurations, and bash blocks for commands. It consistently uses UTC for dated directories and rollovers as requested.
+
+## Security
+No secrets or API keys are included in the documentation. Placeholders and environment variable names are used correctly.
+
+## Quality
+The documentation is clear, well-structured, and includes a static regression test (`tests/test_runbook_generation_backend.py`) to prevent future drift.
